  "detailed_description": "<strong>It has been two days since the once vibrant Air City went completely silent and now it seems to be flying on its own. All attempts to establish contact have failed. A squadron of the best pilots has been dispatched by Capitol City to investigate this sinister silence.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502800/extras/2a0234961b5751620b3071afc4eb53ed.poster.avif?t=1627565406\" width=640 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502800/extras/2a0234961b5751620b3071afc4eb53ed.webm?t=1627565406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502800/extras/2a0234961b5751620b3071afc4eb53ed.mp4?t=1627565406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BRILLIANT PUZZLES</h2>Solve diverse puzzles and riddles in this exclusive escape game!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BEAUTIFUL 3D GRAPHICS</h2>Explore beautiful levels within a captivating game setting.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ATMOSPHERIC AUDIO</h2>The custom soundtrack and ambient sounds complement each other for an immersive experience.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502800/extras/75e76a649704ebee18ce5ec243c07e22.poster.avif?t=1627565406\" width=640 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502800/extras/75e76a649704ebee18ce5ec243c07e22.webm?t=1627565406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502800/extras/75e76a649704ebee18ce5ec243c07e22.mp4?t=1627565406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
